title: Location, Community, Quality Living. It Starts Here!
posting_body: Follow This Link for More Information:
Live in Spacious Kent, Wa Apartment Homes.
This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 905 Sq.
Part of you loves quiet mornings on the deck, tranquil walks through the trees and a soak in the sparkling pools.
A part of you craves action and excitement from the state-of-the art fitness center with indoor activity hub, outdoor basketball court and picnic area with barbecue's.
All that you want, all that you love; put together piece by piece, to create the ideal place to live.
- Modern Clubhouse w/ Lounge Area and TV
- State of the Art Fitness Center w/ Indoor Activity Center
- Fenced Dog Park w/ Seating Area
